The IG resource from SDOH has references to extensions http://hl7.org/fhir/tools/StructureDefinition/ig-parameter and http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/implementationguide-page. I can find the latter only in STU3 and nothing for the first.

@Grahame Grieve Are they in a tools package not picked up by the registry?
anything in the tools space is probably not formally defined. It's on my todo list
the other - not sure. it shouldn't be used if it's not defined?
@Grahame Grieve OK, I've asked the #Gravity sdoh-cc group here.
